data.description: Come check out this well-maintained ranch with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, eat-in kitchen, family room & formal living room & large backyard for entertaining in the spring. This home is conveniently located close to the bases, interstate, outlet shopping, & airport. The HVAC unit was installed in 2019 & the roof was installed 2018 & the upgraded kitchen appliances were purchased in 2020. This home is sure to impress! Call and schedule your showing today!
